column7:
"Thank you @old-envelope for your enthusiasm and @ecru-cooler for your thoughtful suggestion. We appreciate your interest in expanding our forum to include a section for arts, crafts, and cultural heritage. We will explore ways to implement these ideas while ensuring that our forum remains a respectful and inclusive space for all. Let's continue to share our ideas and experiences. Remember, constructive feedback and respectful dialogue are key to our community's growth. 

@ecru-cooler, @old-envelope, and all users, your contributions are valuable. Let's keep the conversation going and look forward to more engaging discussions. 


"
